{"tid":1380554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇到畜龍 第一時間係退 第二時間就要救人！","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:09:11.000Z","uid":275643,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e66b30b5dec06a37058c97a985cdc9af292aec3f","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"少少分享，發夢沙田新城市一役有手足係mtr出少少比班狗壓倒在地，當時前排第一反應係退，但係退唔夠5秒已經有手足大叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>救人！</strong></span></span>，跟住成班手足跳出閘仲要成功救到個位落單手足返陣中。<br />\n<br />\n所以面對畜龍，坦白講佢地只係落單嘅狗，雖然第一時間驚係正常，因為大家都未必有心理準備滅龍，但救人從來都係我地嘅原則之一。所以前線手足見到有人落單就要即叫救人然後湧上去，咁未嘗唔係一個好方法！ 當然，裝備升級係好重要啦"},{"pid":"a8a75c479c6756b4c5249a3ac936f6563e47d14c","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"985b914aa7de124f33434dc51bb75c8bef009a0c","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e15942520beaf7a43fdae817a9ee3c0bd49f839d","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:59:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb6578bc435eb50acc3f7c7f4afc96e5b9899f18","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f19aeca0d35271f5bbf1fef438f2fed52cca0e7","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d64fdee2fbbfdc03337d706b6a221aa1195db468","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>救人！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1321dcdce824c9cda8336062b90c72b794bbc430","tid":1380554,"uid":275643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"大家有意識上去救返手足係好重要"}]}